Extract your favorite frames from a video, with an intuitive and clean interface. 

Features: 
- displays the list of videos saved in your device; 
- tap the screen to start and stop the playback; 
- play the video frame by frame, at half speed or normal speed (forward or reverse mode);
- select the start point with your finger or by using the slider;
- crop the video frame;
- rotate the video in portrait or landscape mode (rotation gesture);
- fill or fit the video within the layer’s bounds and preserve the aspect ratio (pinch gesture);
- save/share the selected video frame.
